sprintf

public static final java.lang.String sprintf(java.lang.Object[] args)
The familiar C-language sprintf rendered in Java and extended for some Grappa types.

Parameters:
args - the first element of this array is a string giving the format of the returned string, the remaining elements are object to be formatted according to the format.
Returns:
a string giving a formatted representation of the arguments.
